cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM

This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with image segmentation. The use of robotic instruments and medical devices also suggests that it could belong to the robotics (cs.RO) sub-category. Machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) are also likely sub-categories as the paper mentions the use of popular CNN architectures for segmentation. Finally, multimedia (cs.MM) could also be a possible sub-category as the paper deals with endoscope images.
